      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Consolidation / Archive Candidates\nOnce this master roadmap is the canonical doc, you can keep only:\n- `edgeLayoutRoadmap.node` (detailed phase-by-phase)\n- `elkEdgesLayoutMaster.node` (this file)\n- `edgeFeaturesShowcase.node` (demo)\n\nCandidates to archive/remove after review:\n- `elkIntegration.node` (superseded by Phase 0\u20132)\n- `elkEdgeRouting.node` (superseded by Phase 3 + demo)\n- `layoutInfo.node` (merged vocabulary/rules into this roadmap)\n\nTip: move older graphs into a subfolder like `public/Roadmaps/_archive/` instead of deleting."
      }
    },
    {
